Puffy walks out during "War Pigs" due to taunts from the band about his playing. He had hurt his ribs during bungee jumping in New Zealand. Patton takes over drums on the song.

This is a recording from the original broadcast to a Metal tape and kept safe for many many years. It was converted a few years ago to MP3 - sorry, no idea where the tape is now, so this is what there is! It includes the Nestles ad performance that has not been broadcast again.
